Package application.Entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DumbTargetingEnemy
    Creates an enemy that will always try and get closer to the player regardless if there is an obstacle in the way.
    Entity
    Super class of all entities classes.
    Player
    player class that stores player's inventory
    Profile
    Represents a profile which can be used throughout the program.
    SimpleEnemies
    Super class of the simple enemies that aren't affected by the player.
    SmartTargetingEnemy
    Creates an enemy that uses path finding to move closer to the player if the enemy has a path to the player.
    StraightLineEnemy
    Creates an enemy that moves in a straight direction and reverses the direction when hitting an object.
    TargetEnemies
    Super Class of the enemies that target the player.
    WallFollowingEnemy
    Creates an enemy that follows the wall so if possible the enemy will always turn left or right at a junction.
